\sum_{k=1}^{\infty} \log(1+\frac{1}{k^2})
|\sum_{k=1}^{\infty} \log(1+\frac{1}{k^2})| \le \sum_{k=1}^{\infty} \log|1+\frac{1}{k^2}| \le \sum_{k=1}^{\infty} 1+\frac{1}{k^2} = \sum_{k=1}^{\infty} 1 + \sum_{k=1}^{\infty}\frac{1}{k^2}
\sum_{k=1}^{\infty} 1+\frac{1}{k^2} = \sum_{k=1}^{\infty} 1 + \sum_{k=1}^{\infty}\frac{1}{k^2}
\sum 1
|\sum_{k=1}^{\infty} \log(1+\frac{1}{k^2})| \le \sum_{k=1}^{\infty} \log|1+\frac{1}{k^2}| \le \sum_{k=1}^{\infty} \frac{1}{k^2}
\sum \frac{1}{k^2}
\sum 1
